name: Sled 45 degree Leg Press Back POV Hips
remarks: Ensure proper alignment of knees and feet to prevent injury. Maintain a controlled motion throughout the exercise.

name: Sled 45 degree Leg Press Side POV Hips
remarks: Focus on even distribution of weight across both legs. Keep your back flat against the sled.

name: Sled 45 degree Leg Press Hips
remarks: Maintain a steady pace and avoid locking your knees at the top of the movement.

name: 45 Side Bend Waist
remarks: Perform with a slow and controlled motion to engage the oblique muscles effectively.
